egii <b>phrase match<\/b>.<\/li>\n<li><b>Testuj i optymalizuj<\/b> \u2013 Regularnie analizuj wyniki swoich kampanii i wprowadzaj zmiany w oparciu o uzyskane dane. Testowanie r\u00f3\u017cnych s\u0142\u00f3w kluczowych pomo\u017ce Ci znale\u017a\u0107 najskuteczniejsze kombinacje.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skuteczne kampanie <b>phrase match<\/b> wymagaj\u0105 przemy\u015blanej strategii oraz ci\u0105g\u0142ej analizy danych. Dzi\u0119ki powy\u017cszym wskaz\u00f3wkom zwi\u0119kszysz szanse na sukces swoich dzia\u0142a\u0144 reklamowych na Amazonie.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak skutecznie ustawi\u0107 kampanie typu phrase match na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Chcesz zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 efektyw<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4872,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4871","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4871"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4871"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4871\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4872"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4871"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories